Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:39.16,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,500)\pos(630,467)}Mentiroso {manga title 856}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.38,0:01:42.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.66,0:01:45.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ouvi um barulho alto vindo de lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:46.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem foi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:50.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi ali?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.75,0:01:55.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que diabos...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.75,0:01:57.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,B-Bobbin-sama!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:01.85,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,505)\fad(538,0)}GUERREIRO (BISPO) DOS PIRATAS DE BIG MOM
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:02:01.85,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,720)\fad(538,0)}BOBBIN, O ECONOMIZADOR - RECOMPENSA: 105.5 MILHÕES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:01:59.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E esse buraco na parede?!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:04.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que aconteceu aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quem fez isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:07.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:08.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,M-Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se aproximem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.82,0:02:15.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bobbin-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:30.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não se preocupem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:34.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu vou cuidar disso com minhas próprias mãos.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:39.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu nunca vou perdoar isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nas festas de chá da mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:44.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...até o próprio diabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:47.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...aparece!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:55.02,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1140,370)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(282,0)}MIRRO WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espelhinho, espelhinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:02:59.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De nada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.84,0:03:01.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.35,0:03:06.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tem algo enorme perto do Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.68,0:03:13.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pode ser...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.51,0:03:19.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que situação...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esse lugar é...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:31.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que vocês vão fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.32,0:03:33.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essa sala...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:40.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...é a da nossa mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.93,0:03:43.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Da Big Mom, a Yonkou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que fazemos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:48.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bom que ele ainda está vivo, mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.05,0:03:53.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não pensei que ele estaria naquele lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.47,0:03:59.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas por que ela está dormindo abraçada com ele?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.72,0:04:03.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook também está dormindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:04.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como ele consegue dormir assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:07.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acorda, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É inútil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele não nos ouve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:18.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É uma criatura estranha de puro osso.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.70,0:04:20.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mama não vai deixá-lo ir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas não se preocupem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:26.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vou fazer ela soltá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.30,0:04:29.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sou a Brûlée!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.91,0:04:30.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Chu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:32.71,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Chu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:33.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tapem suas bocas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.21,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Electro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.06,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A Big Mom não acordou, né?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:53.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela ainda está dormindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:59.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:01.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela nos viu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:12.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, uma mosca!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:25.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:26.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê? O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:27.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que está acontecendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:29.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele acordou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqui, aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:33.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vem rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.79,EnmedioArriba,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, uma mosca.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:42.53,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não durma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:44.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que foi, mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:46.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ataque inimigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.40,0:05:48.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estava dormindo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:50.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Maldita seja!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aí está você!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.57,0:05:53.87,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Aí está você!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que poder de destruição!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.14,0:06:41.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como vamos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...salvar...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.09,0:06:45.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...o Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:48.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...desses monstros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, espera!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:05.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não é sua comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.50,0:07:16.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.09,0:07:19.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Preciso entregar isso a alguém, custe o que custar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.13,0:07:27.42,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(282,0)}MIRRO WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:34.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,E se colocarmos mais cabelo?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.79,0:07:37.54,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, que tal assim?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:39.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim, está ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.68,0:07:41.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Onde encontraram isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:44.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Na sala de execuções do castelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:47.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Usamos algas da cozinha\N para fazer o afro.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pronto, está terminado.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.19,0:07:54.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece muito com o Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:55.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É idêntico!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:57.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se pudermos trocar por isso,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:08:01.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não acho que ela vai perceber que \Nnós o levamos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:08.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Além disso, se colocarmos a \NBrûlée no meio do espelho,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:12.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,poderemos entrar e sair do \Nespelho quando quisermos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:14.96,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Malditos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:16.97,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Vocês vão pagar por isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:20.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com isso, terminamos os preparativos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos começar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:25.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O plano para resgatar o Brook!
Comment: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:28.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Primeiro desafio!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.49,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom, já vou indo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.49,0:08:33.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tome cuidado, Chormano!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.68,0:08:36.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deixa comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Idiota! {SC823 11:53:40}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.65,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Idiota! {SC823 11:53:40}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:15.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.39,0:09:17.52,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu estava com muito medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:19.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Chormano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.26,0:09:21.45,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que alguém mais terá que ir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bom, deixa comigo agora!
Comment: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:27.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Segundo desafio!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.22,0:09:37.18,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:40.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook, Brook, acorde.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:42.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Estou falando com você, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.13,0:09:42.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:44.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A bolha de meleca está se aproximando!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.39,0:09:45.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Fuja!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.27,0:09:55.61,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Será que ele me viu?!
Comment: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:58.28,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Staaare...{line missing in SC}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.12,0:10:01.03,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ele está me olhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:09.29,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:11.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um coelho de pelúcia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:12.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não vai funcionar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:20.50,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, um coelho de pelúcia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:22.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Funcionou?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Essa é sua chance, Carrot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.14,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Dessa vez eu consigo..
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mosca ainda está viva?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.84,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que mosca persistente!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:55.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu estava com muito medo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.56,0:10:57.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.78,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Alguém mais terá que ir de novo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.78,0:11:01.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que patético.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:02.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nesse caso...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.63,0:11:05.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a minha vez! {tive que mover alguns milissegundos o início da animação porque, se não o fizesse, haveria 1 frame que não conseguiria cobrir, então pode parecer um pouquinho diferente, mas acho que é super mínimo}
Comment: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge 3!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:07.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Terceiro desafio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.08,0:11:18.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:20.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei, acorde!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.23,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.62,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ele está sonhando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.76,0:11:36.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é perfeito. {cortei "mas" da linha do SC, já que essa parte foi cortada no ritmo}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:38.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele se afastou das mãos da Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.38,0:11:40.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Certo, eu vou!
Comment: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.31,0:11:42.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quarto desafio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.43,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook, acorde!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:53.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:11:56.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sou eu, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:01.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Um fantasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.30,0:12:08.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ainda está aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.80,0:12:12.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:16.13,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Malvada mosca!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Heavenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.26,0:12:22.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...Feuer!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.75,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,3550,4050)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.75,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,3550,4050)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.75,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3550,4050)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.75,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,3550,4050)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.75,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,3550,4050)}Fogo celestial.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:37.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles conseguiram!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:46.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:52.88,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O plano foi um sucesso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.88,0:12:54.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Viva!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.83,0:12:57.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que bom, que bom!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Hã?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:28.78,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(160,390)\fad(300,300)}SUBÚRBIOS\N DE SWEET CITY {apenas ritmo no infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.79,0:13:33.47,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Parece que ele causou um alvoroço, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:51.89,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Esse cara já está acabado!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:58.65,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Capturamos o Chapéu de Palha\N Luffy e a Gata Ladrona-nasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:03.69,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Luffy lutou contra um oficial inimigo a noite toda para poder vir aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:06.07,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Seu corpo já...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.18,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mas...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:12.37,Pensante,,0,0,0,,...você disse que esperaria aqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:17.71,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Onde você está, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.04,0:14:30.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.77,0:14:35.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que...! {SC824 3:43:36}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:36.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:40.81,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que susto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:42.61,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:42.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.99,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tu...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo isso aconteceu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.36,0:14:49.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não, você nos assustou!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.91,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Um fantasma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.91,0:14:55.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você gritou no pior momento!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:58.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Muito obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.87,0:15:01.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, que bom que você está vivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:05.12,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, eu pensei que ia morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas eu já estou morto.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:15.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Com tanta segurança naquele lugar,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.48,0:15:19.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,era impossível conseguir uma \Ncópia do Road Poneglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:23.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas fiz você arriscar sua vida.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.04,0:15:26.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Desculpe!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que você está dizendo?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:31.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tudo foi por nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.91,0:15:40.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Como você disse, ao nos infiltrarmos apenas nós dois, tínhamos uma chance mínima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:44.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se tentássemos roubar o Road \NPoneglyph da Big Mom em outra ocasião,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:49.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não poderíamos evitar um confronto \Naberto entre as duas tripulações!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:55.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso era uma missão que tínhamos que tentar, mesmo que parecesse impossível!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aqui está a cópia.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.86,0:16:09.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas, Pedro-san, que \Nbom que você está bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:10.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Cópia...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.36,0:16:11.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:18.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu estava tão desesperado que só pensei em pedir para você ser a isca.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:20.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Espera, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.16,0:16:22.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não me diga que isso é...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.58,0:16:25.37,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É a cópia do Poneglyph.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:28.55,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.24,0:16:32.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Assim que terminei a terceira folha...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:35.18,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,apareceu nada mais nada menos \Ndo que a Big Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.98,0:16:42.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você conseguiu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:48.16,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Tinha até um general doce!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:50.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mesmo contra todos esses guardas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:17:01.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O Poneglyph da Big Mom que\N os outros Yonkou tanto desejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.24,0:17:03.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sério...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.67,Pensante,,0,0,0,,O que eles disseram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.67,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,O que eles disseram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:16.64,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Ele disse que roubou nosso Poneglyph?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:19.35,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.72,0:17:25.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É um milagre!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.44,0:17:32.44,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A sala do tesouro é um lugar onde nem mesmo seus familiares podem entrar facilmente.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:34.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você é um homem admirável!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, você poderia me mostrar seus pei...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.93,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.93,0:17:41.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seus ossos quebraram de novo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.08,0:17:44.86,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Então, conseguimos \Num dos nossos objetivos!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Só falta recuperar o Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.34,0:18:35.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?! {SC824 10:55:63}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.38,0:18:37.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nenhum dos dois está aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.14,0:18:38.46,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:42.14,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fs24\pos(1150,370)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(250,250)}MIRRO WORLD
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.46,0:18:41.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles passaram há um tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.28,0:18:42.92,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora não estão mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nem no quarto do Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:47.39,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, tem um cara estranho \Ndormindo no lugar dele.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:49.25,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.25,0:18:51.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Acho que sei onde ele está.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.36,0:18:54.57,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele está do lado de fora, \Nentão não há espelhos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:57.94,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,De manhã, Luffy e Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...brigaram naquele lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:05.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.95,0:19:10.67,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy e Sanji brigaram?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:12.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:17.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji é um Vinsmoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.26,0:19:23.85,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele deve ter vindo por uma razão.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:27.59,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não acho que seja tão simples recuperá-lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.44,0:19:32.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas se queremos recuperá-lo, \Nprecisamos nos apressar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.90,0:19:37.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu ia contar quando estivéssemos\N todos reunidos, mas a verdade é que...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:41.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...se o casamento acontecer amanhã,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:43.87,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não será uma simples cerimônia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:46.62,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O que você quer dizer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:51.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vocês viajaram com o Pekoms, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, o Pekoms!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.08,0:19:54.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ele está bem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:57.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nos separamos durante a viagem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2500,3000)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2500,3000)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2500,3000)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2500,3000)}Virem-se.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.13,0:19:57.80,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Virem-se
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:03.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim, mas ele se envolveu na \Nconspiração de um certo homem,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:05.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,e quase foi comido por tubarões.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:07.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Conspiração?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:08.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.42,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se não tivéssemos percebido,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:16.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,ele estaria morto.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.11,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1145,370)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(300,300)}SWEET CITY {apenas ritmo no infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.78,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fs19\pos(1150,425)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fad(300,300)}6º ANDAR: \N QUARTO DE \NHÓSPEDES BAUM {apenas ritmo no infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,S-Será que eles são...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.83,0:20:29.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...monstros?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.97,0:20:32.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Que patético.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,As garçonetes não deveriam ficar bêbadas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:46.47,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Seria melhor se tivessem enviado\N a companheira do Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Te entendo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.91,0:20:49.70,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,A mulher chamada Nami, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:52.02,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu gosto de garotas de personalidade forte.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.04,0:20:56.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Parece que a Big Mom a capturou.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:59.82,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos perguntar se eles a entregam amanhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.88,0:21:09.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, não devemos beber demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:11.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Amanhã à noite haverá uma festa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:17.40,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Depois que Germa conseguir\N o apoio da Big Mom, a Yonkou,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.40,0:21:21.05,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,conquistaremos o North Blue novamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.05,0:21:24.17,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nosso glorioso Germa \Nfoi desprezado...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:28.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...e humilhado pelos detestáveis\N países do North Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:32.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Logo chegará o dia da nossa vingança!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:36.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Amanhã celebraremos antecipadamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:45.20,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Aquele fracasso que só tinha sido\N uma desgraça para os Vinsmoke...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.20,0:21:48.56,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...nos foi útil!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,É verdade!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:53.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O peixe que pegamos usando \No Sanji como isca é enorme!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.01,0:21:57.10,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quando os inimigos virem a bandeira da Big Mom na frota de Germa,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:58.83,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,eles perderão o ânimo para lutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.83,0:22:03.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agora poderemos conquistar\N o mar com mais firmeza.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.27,0:22:06.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Devemos agradecer ao Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:09.30,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Agradecer ao Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.94,0:22:14.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por aquele fracasso!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:16.60,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Pelo inútil que nos serviu para algo!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.14,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Saúde!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.60,0:22:19.14,Enmedio2,,0,0,0,,Saúde!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.62,0:22:28.54,Denden,,0,0,0,,Ninguém deve entrar em contato com os Vinsmoke\N até o chá da festa de amanhã.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.54,0:22:29.90,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Entendido.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:32.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Já enviei soldados para\N o terceiro andar da enfermaria...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:34.32,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...onde está Reiju-sama.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.12,0:22:34.33,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\pos(645,485)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(600,0)}EM FRENTE AO QUARTO \NDE CONVIDADOS DOS VINSMOKE {apenas ritmo no infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.33,0:22:36.20,Denden,,0,0,0,,Não baixem a guarda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:37.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:41.22,Denden,,0,0,0,,Os Vinsmoke não escaparão de seu destino.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.22,0:22:43.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Não fale demais!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:45.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.54,0:22:54.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Droga...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.52,0:22:58.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Esses desgraçados...!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.93,0:23:40.85,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\fs22\pos(1150,400)}{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(300,300)}NOS ARREDORES \N DA CIDADE {apenas ritmo no infobox}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:54.20,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sumam daqui, piratas de merda!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.28,0:24:30.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sanji...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.65,0:24:43.75,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu não te disse para me esperar.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.52,0:24:46.67,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu me recuso!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.51,0:24:55.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Coma se puder.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.86,0:24:59.72,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Comida...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.46,0:25:07.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ela caiu no caminho...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.95,0:25:10.69,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Está amassada e molhada pela chuva.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.59,0:25:23.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu sou um fracasso, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.94,0:25:46.65,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Deliciosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.06,0:26:03.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Isso é ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.79,0:26:08.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,São todas as nossas comidas favoritas!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.00,0:26:11.71,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Queria que eles também comessem isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.93,0:26:17.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.76,0:26:20.01,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Delicioso, delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.94,0:26:22.56,Pensante,,0,0,0,,Mentiroso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.32,0:26:30.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Ah, estava delicioso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.04,0:26:32.36,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quase me sequei completamente!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.54,0:26:38.04,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se já terminou, vá embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.95,0:26:41.24,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas o que você está dizendo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.24,0:26:42.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos voltar juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.01,0:26:47.79,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Primeiro:
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.50,0:26:54.22,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu insultei meu capitão, que se\N deu ao trabalho de vir me buscar.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.22,0:26:57.97,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você não resistiu e ainda assim \N eu te ataquei com todas as minhas forças.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.18,0:27:05.38,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso não posso mais voltar para o seu navio.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.33,0:27:11.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Segundo:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.71,0:27:17.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,O velho filho da puta, a quem devo\N tanto, e o lugar onde cresci,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.80,0:27:20.26,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Baratie, o restaurante flutuante,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.26,0:27:22.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,foram tomados como reféns\N por precaução.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.62,0:27:31.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por isso não posso fugir do casamento.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.34,0:27:42.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Terceiro:
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.73,0:27:47.08,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,488)}Minha família biológica malvada caiu\N na armadilha da Big Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.14,0:27:51.27,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Em algumas horas, todos estarão mortos.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.62,0:28:02.24,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Se você não fugir, tudo\N será resolvido pacificamente, Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.95,0:28:12.46,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Meu pai e meus irmãos...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.46,0:28:15.34,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...não devo nada a eles.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.34,0:28:17.76,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eles são escória que eu só odeio!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.84,0:28:24.97,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Você é um fracasso que merece morrer!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.97,0:28:28.81,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Nunca se atreva a dizer a ninguém...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.30,0:28:33.36,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,...que eu sou seu pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.36,0:28:36.67,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,É uma desgraça que\N não quero que ninguém saiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.93,0:28:42.48,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.72,0:28:46.03,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...não posso...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.38,0:28:55.64,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...abandoná-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.18,0:29:16.73,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Por essas três razões, \Nnão posso voltar com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.11,0:29:28.91,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Se entendeu, vá embora.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.52,0:30:38.19,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Peça!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.42,0:30:53.69,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.69,0:30:55.04,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.04,0:30:57.40,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Cozinha, rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.40,0:31:00.92,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Sanji-kun, o que vamos comer hoje?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.02,0:31:18.89,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Quem roubou a comida?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.65,0:31:21.81,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Eu sabia que foram vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.76,0:31:25.78,Recuerdo,,0,0,0,,Como castigo, não vão comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.51,0:31:49.68,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.68,0:31:51.07,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.64,0:31:57.58,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Quero voltar para o Sunny!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.30,0:32:10.95,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas não tenho coragem de fugir!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.33,0:32:23.31,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Sei que quando o casamento começar,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.32,0:32:27.00,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,não poderei fazer nada sozinho!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.14,0:32:30.66,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Nem mesmo considero minha família...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.56,0:32:34.98,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,...essa escória!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.61,0:32:40.77,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Mas eu...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.36,0:32:46.09,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Eu quero salvá-los!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.07,0:32:58.74,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Bem, é assim que você é.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.48,0:33:05.28,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Você tem a nós!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.28,0:33:07.51,OP Normal2,,0,0,0,,Vamos acabar com o casamento!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.78,0:33:49.24,Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\N Feeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NTiming:\NHalee,\NUmim\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\N Halee\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.65,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:09.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:12.49,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.86,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.86,0:00:16.07,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.58,0:00:28.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}A alegria de nossos corações colidindo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:35.76,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...e a tristeza ao secar as lágrimas de alegria...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:43.35,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...conecte-as e ondule-as...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.73,0:00:50.23,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...no topo deste vento.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:53.19,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você parou de buscar?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:56.57,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Por que você continua lutando sozinho?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:00:59.87,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ei, para qual futuro você se preparou?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:03.37,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Você já realizou seu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:07.38,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Meus sentimentos por você batem intensamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:11.00,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se o que você busca...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:14.22,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}...é ter um poder sem limites,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:16.55,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}então mostre nossos laços inalteráveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:17.80,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Somos a esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.05,0:01:20.85,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Nos confins deste enorme mundo azul,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:23.89,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}há um lugar onde quero ir com você.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.89,0:01:26.64,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Se há uma rota para chegar lá,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.64,0:01:33.28,English - OP20,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}já decidimos isso há muito tempo.
